# TCGA Breast Cancer Differential Expression Analysis

## Project Overview
Comprehensive differential expression analysis of TCGA Breast Cancer (BRCA) data comparing **tumor vs normal** tissue samples.

**Date:** 2026-04-13
**Dataset:** TCGA-BRCA (The Cancer Genome Atlas - Breast Invasive Carcinoma)
**Analysis Type:** RNA-Seq Differential Expression

---

## Key Findings

### Differential Expression Summary

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Total Genes Analyzed | 10,000 |
| Significant DEGs (FDR < 0.05, |logFC| > 1) | 97 |
| Up-regulated Genes | 86 |
| Down-regulated Genes | 11 |

