---

## Methods

### Statistical Analysis
- **Differential expression:** Two-tailed t-test (unequal variance)
- **Multiple testing correction:** Benjamini-Hochberg FDR
- **Significance thresholds:** FDR < 0.05, |log2 Fold Change| > 1

### Visualization
- **PCA:** Principal Component Analysis for sample clustering
- **Volcano plot:** -log10(p-value) vs log2 fold change
- **Heatmap:** Z-score normalized expression of top DEGs

---

## Clinical Implications

| Gene | Clinical Application |
|------|---------------------|
| ERBB2 (HER2) | Trastuzumab (Herceptin) target |
| ESR1 | Tamoxifen/endocrine therapy marker |
| MKI67 (Ki-67) | Proliferation index for prognosis |
| TOP2A | Anthracycline sensitivity |
| PTEN | PI3K inhibitor sensitivity |

